// Auto-load images dynamically (no extensions hardcoded)
function tryLoad(slot, base, exts){
if(!exts.length) return;
const ext = exts[0];
const img = new Image();
img.onload = ()=>{ slot.innerHTML=''; slot.appendChild(img); };
img.onerror = ()=> tryLoad(slot, base, exts.slice(1));
img.src = `${base}${ext}`;
img.alt = base;
}
document.querySelectorAll('.img-slot[data-img]').forEach(slot=>{
const base = slot.getAttribute('data-img');
tryLoad(slot, base, ['.webp','.png','.jpg','.jpeg']);
});
